Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.64,0:00:12.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すべてをのみ込む\N究極のモンスターマシン ｢沼｣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.84,0:00:12.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The ultimate monster machine which swallows all who challenge it! The Bog!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.02,0:00:15.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Its gates slam shut with a force which drives men to despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.08,0:00:15.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶望的に固く閉ざされたその扉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.92,0:00:18.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だがしかし 何としても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:22.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But! But!!! Against it, Kaiji and his ragtag band make their move!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.29,0:00:22.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを押し開かんと動き出す\Nカイジたち
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.76,0:00:31.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼もう！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.86,0:00:30.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.37,0:00:35.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さ… 坂崎さん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.54,0:00:33.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sakazaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.35,0:00:38.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,550)\pos(640,505)}All-in Bluff
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.50,0:00:37.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's with that outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.54,0:00:39.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その格好は一体？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:44.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The man known as Kotaro Sakazaki faces his final challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.41,0:00:43.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,男 坂崎孝太郎\N今宵 最後の勝負に来た
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.91,0:00:47.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,明鏡止水　精進潔斎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.07,0:00:47.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,My mind clear as water, bright as a mirror! My body purified!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.18,0:00:50.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,天佑神助　寵愛一身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.21,0:00:52.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,By the grace of God, I shall grasp victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.05,0:00:52.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これこそ勝利への道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.02,0:00:55.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,邪念を封じ 仏のご加護
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:00:55.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Seal away wicked thoughts, and throw myself upon Buddha's protection!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:00:58.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,May the will of the gods and Buddha himself flow through my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:01:00.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神仏の念波 我が身に降臨す\Nわしは勝つ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.74,0:01:00.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I will win!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.19,0:01:02.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょ… ちょっと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.38,0:01:01.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.43,0:01:06.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ　また沼に挑戦するだと？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.53,0:01:06.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's trying the Bog again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:10.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's that annoying old guy again. What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.03,0:01:10.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ 性懲りもなくあのクソオヤジ\Nどうしましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.40,0:01:13.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフ　まあ いいじゃないか\Nやらせてやれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:14.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Let him at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:17.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,去る者追わず 来る者拒まずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:17.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No sense in being ungracious hosts. {yes i know the proverm, no it doesn't work in english.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:20.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たぶん残った金の\N持っていき場がないんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.66,0:01:21.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't think he has any other idea what to do with the rest of his money.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.88,0:01:24.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全部 吐き出さなければ\N収まりがつかない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.01,0:01:24.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He probably won't be satisfied until he's broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.08,0:01:26.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,哀れなギャンブルジャンキー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.13,0:01:26.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Such a pitiful gambling junkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.54,0:01:27.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Let him try.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.55,0:01:29.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,受け入れてやれ\Nはっ はあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.85,0:01:30.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.12,0:01:31.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かりました　あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.06,0:01:32.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負 勝負！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.47,0:01:33.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,C'mon, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.99,0:01:36.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かったよ\N受けりゃいいんだろ 受けりゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.10,0:01:36.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine, if you wanna lose that bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:40.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.33,0:01:45.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前回と同じく厳しい\N磁気チェックを受けた坂崎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.41,0:01:44.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just like before, they diligently check Sakazaki for magnets.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:55.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Seriously? After how much he lost last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:52.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おいおい マジかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.48,0:01:55.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この前 あれだけ\N大負けしてんのによう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:20.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうおっしゃってくださいますか\Nあっ そう？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:20.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Please! Give me some good news!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:24.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Thank you! Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:22.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.48,0:02:24.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:28.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何 考えてんだ\Nヤバいぞ あのオヤジ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:26.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's he up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.34,0:02:28.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The old man's gone nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:33.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Amid the onlookers' misgivings, Sakazaki buys his balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.28,0:02:31.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見物人たちの疑念が渦巻く中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.12,0:02:36.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,坂崎 受け取る\N300万のパッキーカード２枚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:36.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Two 3-million packy cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.47,0:02:55.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,坂崎 手持ち600万\Nリベンジ開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:54.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sakazaki attempts his revenge with six million on hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.27,0:03:26.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.36,0:03:25.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:30.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつ 打ってない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.75,0:03:29.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's not serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:34.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見せかけだ\N勝つ気で打っていない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:33.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's putting on a show, not playing to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:39.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この男 何を考えている？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:39.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's he trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:55.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ 店長　どうしたんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:55.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:07.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,坂崎の熱を直に確かめようと\N近づく一条　だが…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:06.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ichijou approaches Sakazaki to gauge his passion in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:07.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:09.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:09.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,伝わらない\Nはあ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.88,0:04:14.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴の体から勝つことへの執念
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:13.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't feel any desire to win from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:17.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気迫が感じられない\Nそう思わないか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:16.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No desire at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:17.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:20.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ　そういえば始める前に
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:24.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's been going on about putting his wickedness behind him since he got here....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:24.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何かもう 邪念はないみたいな\Nことを言ってましたから…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.56,0:04:28.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカが！\Nあるわけねえだろ そんなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:28.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:32.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつらは死ぬまで亡者なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.71,0:04:31.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Men like him don't let go of their lusts until the day they die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:35.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But this unease...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:35.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とはいうものの この違和感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:40.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,漠然とした不安も\N何ら心配する事態にはなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:40.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This gambler's instinct comes to nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:44.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,坂崎は ただただ無為に玉を消費
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:44.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sakazaki fruitlessly empties his balls into the machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:47.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,またたく間に300万を失う
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:46.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In the blink of an eye, he loses three million!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.03,0:04:59.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カーッ　南無 南無 南無！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:59.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Amen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:03.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敗北の坂を\Nまっしぐらに転げ落ちる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:02.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sakazaki tumbles down the cliffs of defeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.75,0:05:11.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I must have been worrying too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:11.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,思いすごしか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.75,0:05:14.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,開始から わずか７分後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:20.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In only seven minutes, Sakazaki runs out of balls having never reached the third tray!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:17.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３段クルーンに\N一度も届くことさえなく
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:20.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,打ち尽くす　すべてを
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:26.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あーあ いいとこないじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:26.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Aww, that wasn't much of a show.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:29.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全然ダメ　何これ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:28.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A complete waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:29.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.33,0:05:32.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,終わりましたね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:30.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:34.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分からん　燃えもせず
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:36.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't get it. Was he playing just to lose, not even for the excitement?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.97,0:05:37.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ負けるために打ったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:41.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それとも燃えていたのか あれで？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.45,0:05:40.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Or was the losing what did it for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:45.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それとも まさか\N俺の目がくもって？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:46.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Or could I be blind to what he's—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:51.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,インチキ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:50.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It cheats!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.32,0:05:54.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,インチキ　インチキ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:54.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It cheats! It cheats!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:58.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめろ！\Nこの台はイカサマ… イカサマだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:55.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.61,0:05:58.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This machine is rigged!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.13,0:06:03.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You! You're the part that does it! Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:06:03.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここだ　ここが諸悪の根源\N死ね！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:05.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカ野郎　何しやがる この…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.51,0:06:04.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:05.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:09.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,放せ　放しやがれ\Nみんな 聞いてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.79,0:06:07.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Let go! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:11.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Listen up, everyone! This casino is a total scam!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:12.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このカジノは\Nとんでもないインチキ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.77,0:06:17.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This machine's remote-controlled!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:17.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今やっつけたこいつが\N店の遠隔操作で玉をはじく仕組み
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.15,0:06:20.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This casino's a ripoff!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.28,0:06:20.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここは いかさまカジノなんだ！\Nインチキ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.42,0:06:23.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Shut him up and bring him to the office!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.51,0:06:23.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黙らせろ！事務所へ連れてけ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.85,0:06:26.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっさと立て　ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:25.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:30.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰が行くか　今日は\Nこのインチキ台と心中…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:32.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've not going anywhere! I'm taking this rigged machine down to hell with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:32.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心中だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.26,0:06:38.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああっ　ダイナマイト！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:39.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's got dynamite!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:44.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死んだる　もとより\N死は覚悟の上で来とるんじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:44.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna die! I don't care if I die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:46.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死んだる　死んだる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:46.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll die! I'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.47,0:06:49.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Anyone who wants to come with me, get over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:50.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死にたい奴はかかってこい！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:53.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜだ　こんな事態になっても
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.92,0:06:55.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even now, I can't feel anything from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:57.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ感じない この男の熱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:07:00.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't feel a real acceptance of death!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:59.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に死ぬという迫力を
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:03.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死んだる　死んだる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.03,0:07:02.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll die! I'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:06.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,エセ　見せかけに見える
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:06.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's faking. It's just an act.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:10.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが何のために？\N金を要求するわけでもなく
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:10.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But why? He's not demanding money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.43,0:07:13.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これじゃ ただ注目を浴びるだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:12.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's just trying to draw our attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:17.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,注目？浴びる？しまった！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.81,0:07:16.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Draw our attention... Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:20.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい　主任以外はついてこい\N店長！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:19.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:20.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:25.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安心しろ\Nそのダイナマイトは偽物だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:24.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! That dynamite's fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.35,0:07:28.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,偽物？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.45,0:07:26.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:31.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,熱がなくて当然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:31.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No wonder he wasn't putting any passion into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.14,0:07:35.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He was just a decoy to distract us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:35.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのオヤジは 俺たちの目を\N引きつけるための松明　おとり
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:39.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's really... No, {\i1}they're{\i0} really after—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:40.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴… いや 奴らの本当の狙いは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:58.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やはりいたか　こそ泥が！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:56.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:58.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.01,0:08:01.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こ… こいつ いつの間に？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:00.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,When did he...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:11.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,で 見つかったかい\Nお目当ての物は？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:10.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Did you find what you were looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:15.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フハハ　残念だったな カイジくん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:15.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No? That's too bad, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.06,0:08:17.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが特別に見せてやるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:17.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But I have something special to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.96,0:08:21.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,システムを見れば\N諦めもつくだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:20.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Perhaps when you see our security you'll give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:23.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一条だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.55,0:08:22.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ichijou.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:27.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,声紋確認　指紋確認
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:25.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Voice recognition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:29.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Fingerprint recognition. And a password.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:30.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして暗証番号
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:33.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この３重チェックだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:32.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We have three separate checks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:51.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金の壁 開帳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:51.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A wall of money is unveiled!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:57.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It echoes in Kaiji's mind! Money! Money! Money!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:57.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うなる金　金　金！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:02.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハッ　これが狙いだったんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:02.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Is this what you were after?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:05.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うちみたいな高レートの裏カジノ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:05.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Running a high-rate illegal casino like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:09.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やる以上は\Nそれ相応の現金が手元に必要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.63,0:09:09.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,we need a lot of cash on hand at any given moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:15.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ご明察だ　とすれば その金が\Nカジノのどこかにあると踏んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:14.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And of course, that means it has to be kept somewhere in the casino.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:22.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You nearly forced your way into the office before to look for it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.46,0:09:20.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,以前 半ば強引に君が事務所に\N入ってきたことがあったな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.13,0:09:23.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは その確認だったわけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:26.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,事務所に金庫があるかないかの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.30,0:09:26.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You were trying to find a safe there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:29.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And if it's not in the office, it has to be in the manager's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.57,0:09:30.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,事務所になければ\N残るは この店長室
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:36.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So then you set Sakazaki to make a scene and draw attention while you snuck in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:34.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこで あの坂崎をおとりにして\N我々の目を引きつけ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:36.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君はここに忍び込んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:41.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You were planning to find the safe and come back another day to crack it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:41.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日は金庫の有無を確認し\N後日 改めてアタック
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:43.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:44.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなところだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:48.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残念ながら うちの金庫は\N沼と同様に難攻不落
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.42,0:09:49.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but my safe is just as unbeatable as the Bog.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:51.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(電話の着信音)\N金庫破りなど不可能だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:51.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There's simply no way you'd be able to break in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:56.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい\N店長　坂崎を確保したそうです
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:52.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.47,0:09:56.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Boss! They've got a handle on Sakazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.06,0:09:59.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,連れてくるように言え\Nはい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:57.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Tell them to bring him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.98,0:09:58.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.25,0:10:24.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,店長　ありました\N盗聴器とカメラです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.29,0:10:24.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Boss! We found a bug and a camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:27.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか　燃やせ\Nはっ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:26.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I see. Burn them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.59,0:10:27.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:32.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Now, are you two ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:30.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さて いいかな ２人とも
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:33.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,覚悟は？\Nひーっ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:35.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほれ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:41.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's your turn now! Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.44,0:10:41.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ お前もだ　くらえ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:44.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待て　殴るのはマズい\Nはあ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:42.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.30,0:10:43.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.88,0:10:47.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オヤジの方は\Nどうなろうと かまわないが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:51.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't care what happens to the old man, but Kaiji is going back underground in a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.81,0:10:51.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジくんは あと１週間で\N地下に戻る身だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:55.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,His body is Teiai property.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.55,0:10:56.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり彼の体は\N帝愛にとっては財産
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.18,0:11:01.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If we're so rough with him that he can't work, we'll have to replace him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:10:59.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あまり手荒なことをして\N働けなくなったら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:01.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こちらの責任問題だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:10.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, we certainly can't just let him walk out of here after that attempt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.13,0:11:07.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かといって これだけ\N大それたマネをしでかした者を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:10.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何の制裁もなく\N帰すわけにもいかない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:13.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうする？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:11.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What {\i1}shall{\i0} we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:16.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わ… 分かりました
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:15.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:17.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Drop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:19.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,組み伏せろ！\Nはっ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:18.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:31.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お持ちしました
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.77,0:11:31.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.09,0:11:32.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.09,0:11:34.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし　フフフ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:37.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だと思う？これ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:37.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What do you think this is, Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:40.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,指折りか\Nハハハ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:39.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you going to break my fingers?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:45.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言ったろ ダメなんだって\Nそういう手荒なマネは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.93,0:11:45.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I told you, we're not going to be so rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:48.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is far, far more delicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:50.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは もっと上品な物だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:54.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,First I screw it on like this so it won't come off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:55.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こうして抜けないように\Nセットして
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:58.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとは ここのネジを回せば
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:12:01.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then I turn the other screw, and the needle inside plunges forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:12:02.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,筒の中の針が進むんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:07.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then it tears straight under your fingernail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:05.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょうど爪の わずか下の場所に
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:07.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,メリメリと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:09.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you actually going to—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:09.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様 本気か？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:13.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on, Kaiji. This is no time for jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.96,0:12:13.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいにく冗談は言わないタチでね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.14,0:12:23.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Unimaginable jolts of pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.24,0:12:23.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,想像を絶する痛みを超えた激痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.66,0:12:41.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ　まだたった１本で…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:40.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, but that was just the first finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.16,0:12:47.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見ろ　世にも珍しい\N爪の裏から塗る血のマニキュアだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.25,0:12:47.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Look! How many men do you know with a blood-red manicure below the nail?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:51.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're so lucky to have such a unique look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:51.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなことをする伊達者\Nそうそういないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:52.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Now tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:53.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ 言ってみな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:56.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何本 塗ってほしい？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:56.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How many fingers would you like done today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.39,0:13:07.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just keep walking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:09.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら 歩け　ほら\Nうっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:12.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほうら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:20.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジくん…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:20.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:23.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっさと消えな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:22.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Scram!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:26.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫か カイジくん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:26.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:41.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うおっ　なんて ひでえことを！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:41.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That was terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.79,0:13:47.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソッ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:49.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Goddammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.73,0:13:50.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チキショー　見てろ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.48,0:13:52.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.53,0:13:52.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今に見てろ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:56.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ichijou... Ichijou, you son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:56.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一条… 一条の野郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.47,0:13:58.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後悔させてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:58.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna make you pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:14:04.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you! You're gonna get a taste of your own medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:02.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必ず味わわせてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.28,0:14:05.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺と同じ苦しみ 痛みを！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:08.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ… いつか いつか…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:09.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Someday! Someday! Someday!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:11.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつか！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.17,0:14:13.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Why were you so easy on him, boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.22,0:14:13.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手ぬるかったんじゃ\Nないですか 店長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:16.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと痛めつけておいた方が…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.89,0:14:16.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You should have really taught him a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.19,0:14:19.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That was enough for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.26,0:14:20.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ いいじゃないか\N今回はこの程度で
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:23.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We don't want to accidentally kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:23.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あまり本気を出して\N死なれては困るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:26.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんなクズでも この地上ではな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.58,0:14:26.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even trash like him can't be disposed of like that on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.45,0:14:27.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:30.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴が死ぬのは あくまで地下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:31.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He'll die underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.94,0:14:35.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手ぬるく感じるだろうが\Nこの程度の決着が頃合いさ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.06,0:14:35.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It may seem like going easy on him, but it will have to do for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:44.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その数日後\N破壊された箇所の部品が届き
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:47.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Several days later, replacement parts for the Bog arrive, and it is repaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.85,0:14:47.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沼が修理される
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:54.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうだ？\N問題ありません
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:52.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So how's it working?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:54.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.03,0:14:56.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The replacement parts are working just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.03,0:14:57.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,取り換えた部品も\Nスムーズに動きますし
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:14:59.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The block activates properly as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:14:59.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ブロックも正常に作動しています
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:02.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then we start it up again tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:02.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ今夜から再開だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:06.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,再開された後 カイジたちは現れず
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:06.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even after the Bog returns, Kaiji and the others do not come to play it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:12.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,坂崎のインチキ発言の影響か\N他に打つ者もなく３日目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:12.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Perhaps due to Sakazaki's claim that it's rigged, no one else plays either for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.95,0:15:22.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジが地上にいられる最後の日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:20.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then, Kaiji's last day on the surface arrives!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.49,0:15:24.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沼のクギ調整 終わりました
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:24.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've finished adjusting the Bog's pins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.89,0:15:27.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ご苦労さん　一服してゆけ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:27.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Excellent work. Would you like a cup?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:30.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:30.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ　ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:33.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Everyone has forgotten about Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.46,0:15:34.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰もがカイジのことなど\N忘れていた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:37.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It suddenly just clicked. Later, I'm going to go back—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:39.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,店長！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:38.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:41.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What do we do!? They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:41.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしましょう　来たんですが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:44.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They're back and they haven't learned their lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:45.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,性懲りもなく また奴らが…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:51.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji? He's still on the surface?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:51.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ？\Nこいつ まだ地上にいたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.29,0:15:52.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:56.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ　確か正確なリミットは\N今日の午後４時だったかと
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:55.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,His time runs out today at four in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:57.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フン
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.96,0:16:01.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 ９時だから あと７時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:15:59.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's nine right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:01.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He has seven hours left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:05.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ　玉砕に来たか\N玉砕？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:04.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Looks like he's going out with a bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.51,0:16:05.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Going out with a bang?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.43,0:16:10.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴は地下を出る時 70万だか\N80万だかの小銭をつかんでる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.59,0:16:10.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He came up from the underground with seven or eight hundred thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:12.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そいつを使って 一か八か
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:16.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's desperate. He bet three hundred thousand on roulette.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:16.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うちの36倍ルーレットあたりで\N30万張って
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.81,0:16:19.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たれば1000万
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.86,0:16:19.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If he'd won, that would have been ten million.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:21.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He would have been able to pay off his debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:21.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで奴の借金は完済
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:23.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't have had to go back underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:23.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地下に戻らずに済む
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:27.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフ… バカが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:26.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:29.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなに都合よくいかねえんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:29.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Things aren't going to work out that well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:36.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm disappointed. Even though it's his last chance, he's still relying on luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:34.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガッカリだぜ　いろいろ\N仕掛けてきた最後の最後が結局
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:36.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな運否天賦か
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:38.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:41.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうします？\Nまっ 見届けてやるか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:40.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Let's watch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.40,0:16:44.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後の夢　あがきを…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:44.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Watch him squirm as his dreams die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:52.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ようこそ　カイジ様の\Nこの地上での最後の時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.71,0:16:48.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:58.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm quite honored that you're choosing to spend your last hours on the surface at our casino.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:55.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを当カジノで\Nお過ごしくださるとは
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:58.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,従業員一同 身にあまる光栄です
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:02.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいのかよ\N俺は問題児じゃねえのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:02.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What, are you going to treat me like some troublemaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.36,0:17:05.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんな些細なことは\N水に流しました
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:05.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm letting bygones be bygones.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:11.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ ルーレットでもバカラでも\Nご自由に遊んでいってください
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.80,0:17:10.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Make yourself at home at our roulette or baccarat tables.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:13.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:12.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.11,0:17:28.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,店長　奴ら まさか！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:28.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Boss, I think he's—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.92,0:17:34.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これだ　この沼をやりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.10,0:17:35.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here we go. I want to play the Bog.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:36.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何 言ってんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:40.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you nuts? The Bog isn't for broke-asses like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:41.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これはお前みたいな貧乏人が\N手を出せる代物じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:42.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I have plenty of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:43.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金ならある
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:48.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,5000万　十分だろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:48.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,50 million is enough, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:50.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少しお待ちを
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:49.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.52,0:17:50.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.87,0:17:56.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一体どういうつもりですかね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.97,0:17:56.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's he planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:18:00.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you sure he hasn't done anything to the machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:17:59.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか細工されていないよな\Nこの台
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.98,0:18:04.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい　24時間 必ず誰かが\Nあの台を監視していましたし
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.03,0:18:04.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes. We've had a guard on it 24 hours a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:08.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カメラも回っていました\N誰かが近づくチャンス
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.65,0:18:11.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's on camera too, and the power hasn't gone out or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.32,0:18:11.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,火事や停電のような\Nアクシデントもありませんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.79,0:18:16.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ なぜ奴らは\Nみたび突っ込む？破滅へ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.85,0:18:15.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then why are they trying it a third time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.37,0:18:16.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just to ruin themselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:18.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Shall we stop them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.56,0:18:18.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここは やめておきますか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.60,0:18:22.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,100パーセント出る理由も\N道理もありませんが それでも…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:22.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even if it's rigged to be 100% safe....
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:24.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逃げるのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.90,0:18:28.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you just going to run away because you think there's a little risk?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:30.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっとでもリスクを感じたら\Nもう逃げ出すのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:39.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I thought this casino was supposed to be the home of the undefeatable Bog.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:34.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その程度か\Nこのカジノの売り ｢沼｣ってのは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:38.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対的存在みたいなこと言って
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.15,0:18:40.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,底が割れたな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:45.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ichijou. Act like a manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.79,0:18:45.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一条　しょせんお前は管理人だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:47.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.53,0:18:47.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黙れ 貴様！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:55.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ　その顔だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.47,0:18:56.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's what I want to see. Bring it, Ichijou.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:57.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいよ 一条
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:12.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まっ ここまで勝負を望むからには
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.28,0:19:14.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You've got a lot of confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:17.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か魂胆… 策があるんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:16.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You have a trick up your sleeve, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.29,0:19:19.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正直 皆目分からんが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.35,0:19:19.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:26.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,When a pachinko machine's set up not to pay, skill doesn't matter. Jack shit matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:23.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パチンコってのは一度\N台が出ないと設定されたら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:26.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう打ち方もクソもない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:29.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出ないといったら出ない\N逆に言えば
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.16,0:19:32.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If it won't way, it won't pay, You'd need to modify the machine to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.07,0:19:32.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つためには この台に\N細工をしなければならない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.87,0:19:35.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yet you haven't done that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.87,0:19:36.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なのに その痕跡はないときている
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.24,0:19:38.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうやって勝つ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:38.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How are you going to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.48,0:19:43.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,面白い　逆に興味がわいてきたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:45.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Your strategy—your tricks—have me more and more intrigued.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:46.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その戦略　手品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.29,0:19:50.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや むしろ勘違い\N浅知恵といったところか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:50.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Or am I wrong? Are you really just that dense?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:58.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Very well! I accept your challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:56.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいだろう　受けてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.66,0:19:59.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その挑戦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:04.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ　最初で最後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.58,0:20:07.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji begins his first and last duel with the Bog!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:07.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沼との死闘へ動き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:09.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地上でのラストチャンス
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:13.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is his last chance on the surface! He has only seven hours left on the outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.34,0:20:11.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャバで残された猶予
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.71,0:20:16.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと７時間　420分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.72,0:20:15.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,420 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.32,0:20:35.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No sense in being ungracious hosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.52,0:20:42.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't think he has any other idea what to do with the rest of his money.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:48.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He probably won't be satisfied until he's broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.26,0:20:52.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Such a pitiful gambling junkie.
